configurations.name: Debug //projects/rust_hello_world:rust_hello_world
targetCreateCommands: script import subprocess, os, sys; result = subprocess.run(['bazel', 'run', '--compilation_mode=dbg', '--strip=never', '--run_under=@rules_rust//tools/vscode:get_binary_path', '//projects/rust_hello_world:rust_hello_world'], stdout=subprocess.PIPE, text=True, cwd='${workspaceFolder}'); binary_path = result.stdout.strip().splitlines()[-1]; assert binary_path, 'No binary path output for //projects/rust_hello_world:rust_hello_world'; abs_path = os.path.join('${workspaceFolder}', binary_path); lldb.debugger.CreateTarget(abs_path)
